transcript:
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hello.
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Haan, good morning. Kadir bol raha tha India mein aap.
Customer: Haan, haan, haan.
Executive: Aapne dekh liya subscribe ho gaya?
Customer: Ah, woh mere ko utna idea nahi hai. Bhai abhi thoda bahar gaya hai. Woh aane ke baad mein aapko call karne ke liye bolta hu.
Executive: Kitne baje tak aayenge?
Customer: Abhi aadha ek ghante mein aa jayega.
Executive: Aadhe ghante mein aa jayega. Itni der mein call karega jara.
Customer: Achha, achha, theek hai.
Executive: Theek hai.
